claim.claim-text:
Floor panel (100, 106) for a floor of a passenger cabin (400) of a mobile platform (200), the floor panel comprising:
a base body (100) having a cable channel (106) extending along a longitudinal direction of the base body for accommodating electric cables (305);
a cover element (303, 304) for being arranged on top of the cable channel and a part of top surface of the base body (100) for covering the cable channel (106) and for being attached to the base body;
wherein the base body (100) is realized in the form of a sandwich component that includes two honeycomb structures, the first honeycomb structure (103) extending from a left edge (203) of the base body to a left side (131) of the cable channel (106) and the second honeycomb structure extending from a right edge (204) of the base body to a right side (141) of the cable channel.

Floor panel of one of the preceding claims,

adapted for being arranged between a first seat rail (301) and a second seat rail (302) which is parallel to the first seat rail;

wherein the base body comprises a first attachment region parallel and adjacent to the left edge (203) of the base body for attachment to the first seat rail;

wherein the base body comprises a second attachment region parallel and adjacent to the right edge (204) of the base body for attachment to the second seat rail.
